11. [Prepare SDKs and contract artifacts](/guides/tutorial-writing-ts-services/contract-artifacts)
12. [Declare optional dependencies](/guides/tutorial-writing-ts-services/optional-dependencies)
13. [Use the development loop](/guides/tutorial-writing-ts-services/development-loop)

